title: Jenkins the Valet Yacht Licensing Contract
description:
Agreement between Bostonbob (bb) and AC (ac). 

bb will pay a one time yacht leasing fee of 4 eth to ac.

In return, ac will lease his yacht to bb by submitting bb’s MAYC and his back story in the Jenkins the valet author portal. Ac’s WAGMI Yacht #1047 will be attached to bb’s MAYC #1353, casting 1353 for a role in the book. 

In addition, a royalty split will be put into place between the two parties. 80% for ac/20% for bb (managed and paid out by Jenkins team at a later date)

*All names in contract are Twitter profile names as of 12/8.
